<plot>Our Race follows the development of the Abreast a River Dragon Boat racing team on the East River in New Glasgow. The members are all breast cancer survivors, of all ages and from every part of the community. Shot over the course of five years, this documentary is a loving portrait of the strength, support and power of these women as they connect with the spirit of the dragon and with each other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?417707</url></doc>
